        "Error",
        "Idle",
        "Success",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Success完成后通过Reset回到Idle等待下一次请求。Error这边，Retry是重试机制，Abort则是上报到TelemetryStream后结束。还有，从Idle进入Loading的触发条件是Start Request。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Success",
        "Idle",
        "Error",
        "Loading",
        "Start Request"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主干：PLC_Logic指向Idle，Idle通过Start Request进入Loading。Loading之后分叉，Data Received到Success，Request Failed到Error。Success用Reset回Idle，Error用Retry回Idle，同时Error用Abort连到TelemetryStream。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Start Request",
