        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Loading到Success的触发条件我确认一下——应该是Data Validated更准确，但你们系统里用的是Data Received对吧？那就保持Data Received。另外，Error到TelemetryStream的箭头标签我再看下，应该是Abort而不是Cancel。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Data Received",
        "Error",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "Abort"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，标签保持Data Received和Abort。我核对一下整体结构：PLC_Logic作为起始点，状态流转是Idle→Loading→(Success/Error)，两个终态都能回到Idle，Error额外有Abort出口到TelemetryStream。这样理解正确吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Success",
        "Error",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。注意Idle是双向的——既是入口也是循环回来的汇合点。还有，PLC_Logic和TelemetryStream这两个外部系统用方括号标注，和中间的状态圆角框区分开。",
      "elements_involved": [
